high_descs: Turn right and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge and take the mug out of the fridge.
Turn left and walk to the sink.
Put the mug in the sink, turn the water on and fill the sink.
Take the mug out of the sink, go right to the coffee maker.
Set the mug on the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Bring a washed mug to the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn around and walk up to the fridge
Open the fridge and remove the white mug from it
Turn left and walk to the kitchen sink
Wash the mug under water from the sink and remove it
Turn right and walk a short distance to the coffee maker right of the sink
Put the mug on the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: Put the white mug on the coffee maker

high_descs: Go to the fridge and open it
Take the mug from the fridge
Place the mug in the sink
Wash the mug in the sink
Put the mug in the machine
anns.task_desc: Clean the mug in the fridge and place it in the coffee machine
